    <title>LaTex排版</title>
    <url>/2024/07/21/LaTex%E6%8E%92%E7%89%88/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="LaTeX排版"><a href="#LaTeX排版" class="headerlink" title="LaTeX排版"></a>LaTeX排版</h2><p>最近帮师哥用 LaTeX 排了一篇 Springer Nature 旗下的期刊，第一次用 LaTeX 排版，记录一下遇到的小问题和细节。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h3><p>把图片转成 PDF，再转为 EPS 格式，使用 Inkscape 这个软件，导出格式选择封装的 PostScript，即 EPS。</p>
<h3 id="文档基本设置"><a href="#文档基本设置" class="headerlink" title="文档基本设置"></a>文档基本设置</h3><p><code>[]</code> 里面表示文档类的参数，分别是数学物理格式，双列布局，<code>&#123;&#125;</code> 里面是文档类名称。</p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\documentclass</span>[sn-mathphys-num,iicol]&#123;sn-jnl&#125;<span class="comment">%</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="宏包"><a href="#宏包" class="headerlink" title="宏包"></a>宏包</h3><p>该加的都加进去，只要注意一下不要冲突就行</p>
<h3 id="通讯作者"><a href="#通讯作者" class="headerlink" title="通讯作者"></a>通讯作者</h3><p>带上星号</p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\author</span>*[1]&#123;<span class="keyword">\fnm</span>&#123;Gang&#125; <span class="keyword">\sur</span>&#123;Dong&#125;&#125;<span class="keyword">\email</span>&#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="图片插入"><a href="#图片插入" class="headerlink" title="图片插入"></a>图片插入</h3><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;figure&#125;[htbp]<span class="comment">%</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\centering</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\includegraphics</span>[width=0.85<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>]&#123;fig6.eps&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\caption</span>&#123;The curve of equivalent impedance <span class="built_in">$</span>Zr<span class="built_in">$</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig6&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;figure&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>上面是单图，下面是多张图片：</p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;figure&#125;[htbp]</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\centering</span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;subfigure&#125;&#123;0.85<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;<span class="comment">%%这里一定要写图片缩放比例</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\centering</span>   </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\includegraphics</span>[width=<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>]&#123;fig8a.eps&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\caption</span>&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig8a&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;subfigure&#125;   </span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;subfigure&#125;&#123;0.85<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;<span class="comment">%%这里一定要写图片缩放比例</span></span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\centering</span>   </span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\includegraphics</span>[width=<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>]&#123;fig8b.eps&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\caption</span>&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig8b&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;subfigure&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\caption</span>&#123;The simulation results while changing <span class="built_in">$</span>C<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;pla&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span>. (a) LRQ in PDN design while changing <span class="built_in">$</span>C<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;pla&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span> (b) Impedance profile of the equivalent impedance while changing <span class="built_in">$</span>C<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;pla&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\label</span>&#123;fig8&#125;<span class="comment">%%图表标题一般不加标点</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;figure&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用 <code>subfigure</code> 可以在一个 Fig 里面插入多个子图，自动进行 a，b，c 编号。</p>
<h3 id="公式插入"><a href="#公式插入" class="headerlink" title="公式插入"></a>公式插入</h3><p>使用 SimpleTeX 这个软件，很方便</p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;subequations&#125;<span class="keyword">\label</span>&#123;eq11&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;equation&#125;Z<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;o&#125;(f<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;)=(R<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;+jX<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;)<span class="keyword">\parallel</span> ESR<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\prime</span>&#125;<span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;equation&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;equation&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;split&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> ~~~~~<span class="keyword">\left</span>|Z<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;o&#125;<span class="keyword">\left</span>(f<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="keyword">\right</span>)<span class="keyword">\right</span>|=<span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="keyword">\frac</span>&#123;ESR<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\prime</span>&#125;<span class="keyword">\cdot</span> Z<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="keyword">\sqrt</span>&#123;ESR<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\prime</span>2&#125;+2R<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="keyword">\cdot</span> ESR<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\prime</span>&#125;+R<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;2&#125;+X<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;2&#125;&#125;&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\left</span>(ESR<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\prime</span>&#125;+R<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="keyword">\right</span>)<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;2&#125;+X<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;r&#125;<span class="built_in">^</span>&#123;2&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;split&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;equation&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;subequations&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>使用 <code>subequations</code> 在一个公式块内插入多个公式，</p>
<p>使用 <code>split</code> 创建多行公式</p>
<p>采用 <code>&amp;</code> 可以指定对齐的位置，用 <code>~</code> 当空格占位置</p>
<p>效果</p>
<!-- 请将图片 image.png 放到 source/_posts/LaTex排版/ 文件夹下，然后使用下面的 Markdown 语法来插入图片 -->
<!-- ![图片描述](LaTex排版/image.png) -->


<h3 id="表格插入"><a href="#表格插入" class="headerlink" title="表格插入"></a>表格插入</h3><p>通常使用三线表，<code>\toprule</code>, <code>\midrule</code>, <code>\bottomrule</code></p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;table&#125;[ht]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\centering</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;minipage&#125;&#123;<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;	</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\caption</span>&#123;Typical Parameter Values for PDN&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\label</span>&#123;tab:pdn<span class="built_in">_</span>parameters&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\begin</span>&#123;tabular&#125;&#123;@&#123;&#125;p&#123;0.17<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;p&#123;0.08<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;p&#123;0.08<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;p&#123;0.08<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;p&#123;0.08<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;p&#123;0.08<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;p&#123;0.08<span class="keyword">\columnwidth</span>&#125;@&#123;&#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\toprule</span></span><br><span class="line">Parameter <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="built_in">$</span>R<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;flat&#125;&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="built_in">$</span>L<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;slew&#125;&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="built_in">$</span>R<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;out&#125;&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="built_in">$</span>L<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;out&#125;&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span>  <span class="built_in">$</span>C<span class="built_in">_</span>&#123;<span class="keyword">\text</span>&#123;pla&#125;&#125;<span class="built_in">$</span> <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> <span class="built_in">$</span>Z<span class="built_in">_</span>t<span class="built_in">$</span> <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\midrule</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\multirow</span>&#123;2&#125;&#123;*&#125;&#123;Value&#125;   <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 30   <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 67.5    <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 1  <span class="built_in">&amp;</span>4 <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 2.2    <span class="built_in">&amp;</span> 10  <span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">&amp;</span>m<span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\Omega</span><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">&amp;</span>  nH <span class="built_in">&amp;</span>m<span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\Omega</span><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="built_in">&amp;</span>nH<span class="built_in">&amp;</span> nF<span class="built_in">&amp;</span>m<span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\Omega</span><span class="built_in">$</span><span class="keyword">\\</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\bottomrule</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;tabular&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;minipage&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\end</span>&#123;table&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><code>\multirow&#123;2&#125;&#123;*&#125;&#123;Value&#125;</code> 表示“Value”占两行，这样可以做到表格自动排列不合适情况下自己手动排版。</p>
<p><code>&#123;@&#123;&#125;p&#123;0.17\columnwidth&#125;p&#123;0.08\columnwidth&#125;@&#123;&#125;&#125;</code>，<code>@&#123;&#125;</code> 去掉左右空白，<code>p</code> 设置占用的长度，<code>l</code> 左对齐，<code>c</code> 居中对齐。</p>
<p>效果：</p>
<!-- 请将图片 image.png 放到 source/_posts/LaTex排版/ 文件夹下，然后使用下面的 Markdown 语法来插入图片 -->
<!-- ![图片描述](LaTex排版/image.png) -->


<h3 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h3><p>对图标之类的使用标签，引用的时候用 <code>\ref&#123;&#125;</code>，</p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\bibliography</span>&#123;sn-bibliography&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>指明参考文献引用文件</p>
<p>参考文献注意多用 IEEE Trans，而不是 Access，这个是水刊，引用多用期刊，个别会议。</p>
<h3 id="页面设置"><a href="#页面设置" class="headerlink" title="页面设置"></a>页面设置</h3><p>在 <code>.cls</code> 文件里，双列页面的话，在 <code>\if@iicol</code> 的最后修改数据</p>
<figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">\RequirePackage</span>[<span class="comment">%</span></span><br><span class="line">    reversemp,</span><br><span class="line">    paperwidth=193mm,</span><br><span class="line">    paperheight=260mm,</span><br><span class="line">    top=&#123;19.29mm&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    headheight=&#123;12pt&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    headsep=&#123;5.15mm&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    text=&#123;160mm,216mm&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    marginparsep=5mm,</span><br><span class="line">    marginparwidth=12mm,</span><br><span class="line">    bindingoffset=6mm,</span><br><span class="line">    footskip=10.13mm,twocolumn]&#123;geometry&#125;<span class="comment">%</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>主要修改 <code>paperwidth=193mm</code>, <code>paperheight=260mm</code>。如果是别的页面格式对应修改。</p>
<h3 id="总体目标"><a href="#总体目标" class="headerlink" title="总体目标"></a>总体目标</h3><p>使用 Overleaf 编译的结果没报 error 就算成功，否则最好把 error 消完，如果只需要编译出来的 PDF 文件可以不管。</p>
]]></content>
